a) Amazon S3
b) Amazon EC2
c) Amazon EMR
d) Amazon Redshift

Which AWS service provides a scalable and managed message queue for microservices?
a) Amazon SQS
b) Amazon SNS
c) AWS Lambda
d) Amazon RDS

What is the global content delivery network (CDN) service provided by AWS?
a) Amazon S3
b) Amazon CloudFront
c) Amazon Route 53
d) Amazon VPC

AWS Lambda, introduced in 2014, is a service that allows you to:
a) Deploy Docker containers
b) Run serverless functions
c) Create virtual machines
d) Store and retrieve data

Which AWS database service offers a fully managed in-memory cache?
a) Amazon RDS
b) Amazon Redshift
c) Amazon DynamoDB
d) Amazon ElastiCache

In 2015, AWS announced a new service for Internet of Things (IoT) applications. What is it called?
a) AWS IoT Core
b) AWS IoT Analytics
c) AWS IoT Device Defender
d) AWS IoT Events

Which AWS service provides serverless computing capabilities?
a) Amazon EC2
b) Amazon S3
c) Amazon RDS
d) AWS Lambda

What is the AWS service that helps you create and manage virtual private networks (VPNs)?
a) Amazon VPC
b) Amazon EC2
c) Amazon RDS
d) AWS Direct Connect

Answers:

c) 2006
b) Amazon EC2
c) Amazon EMR
a) Amazon SQS
b) Amazon CloudFront
b) Run serverless functions
d) Amazon ElastiCache
