    A. AWS Auto Scaling
    B. Amazon Kinesis Video Streams
    C. Elastic Load Balancing
    D. Amazon CloudFront


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Amith Bhanudas Aug 8, 12:39
The best option for the company to ensure that users can view videos with low latency would be to use Amazon CloudFront. 

CloudFront is a content delivery network (CDN) that speeds up the delivery of static and dynamic web content, such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and images, as well as videos.

