Correct Answer - C. AWS Service Catalog
Why AWS Service Catalog?
Create, organize, and govern a curated catalog of AWS resources that can be shared at the permissions level so you can quickly 
provision approved cloud resources without needing direct access to the underlying AWS services.
https://aws.amazon.com/servicecatalog/

